" ctrlsf 配置
nmap <leader>cf :CtrlSF<CR>
vmap <leader>cf <Plug>CtrlSFVwordExec
nnoremap <leader>ct :CtrlSFToggle<CR>

" 一键编译
nmap <Leader>m :wa<CR>:make<CR><CR>:botright cwindow<CR>
nmap <Leader>w :botright cwindow<CR>
nmap <leader>j :cn<CR>
nmap <leader>k :cp<CR>

